title: Tempus Procedium
description: Collection of timely articles which were delivered over the many years of the Unariun mission, they are most vitally concerned with all aspects of man's planetary and intergalactic life. A volume in Norman's home study course on cosmology, this volume with material on Unrigs, man vs. television, flashbacks and workouts, the symbolic world, the last supper and the kingdom within, DNA, miracles, false science theories, the laser, false gods and images, sexuality, water and energy conversion, hallucinations, the mongoloid, more.
author: Ernest L. Norman
